{"tid":1555891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌手足要跳閘啦喂","createTime":"2019-09-09T13:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T17:17:35.000Z","uid":201638,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf21947bc080a20b7bb7322c5739fe502e3841d","tid":1555891,"uid":201638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"次次坐狗鐵都冇人跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得自己跳 <br />\n<br />\n今日仲柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住用力推開三棍機 點知部機卡住左<br />\n<br />\n搞到要係粉紅人面前跳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個朋友又係推唔到部機 搞到要跳 <br />\n<br />\n不過我地兩個都突破左個心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後就算有職員都照跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇東涌手足見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果見到我或者朋友 可以搵我地一齊跳架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c47944e5f5a65427df590402d2855f127ab7b6","tid":1555891,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"東涌部個三角位有黑色嘅卡住係推唔到 可以去7-11個邊個闊機跳"},{"pid":"db2db76cef8902c93e3631792817760d9fd440b0","tid":1555891,"uid":201638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c47944e5f5a65427df590402d2855f127ab7b6","tid":1555891,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"東涌部個三角位有黑色嘅卡住係推唔到 可以去7-11個邊個闊機跳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:01: